data.description: Experience the warm welcome of this stunning home nestled in the tranquil woods of Auburn Hills, in the highly sought-after Goddard school district. With 5 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home offers ample space for comfortable living. The highlight is the saltwater pool with a tanning deck, perfect for relaxation and enjoyment. Inside, the open concept design creates a spacious atmosphere, with a large island that is ideal for entertaining guests. This home boasts wood flooring, drop zone, and granite counters in the kitchen, while the master bath dazzles with quartz counters. The family room is expansive and features a wet bar, perfect for hosting gatherings. The walk-out basement adds versatility to the home. With attention to detail, custom shower and barn doors add a touch of elegance. The backyard is truly a showstopper, with a two-tier custom saltwater pool installed in 2020, making it the ideal setting for summer get-togethers. Additional updates include a new roof in 2019. And to complete the luxurious experience, a 7-seater hot tub awaits you.
